# Claude Development Framework - .gitignore

# ============================================
# User's Stack Customizations
# ============================================
# Note: .claude/your-stack/ contains example/template configurations
# Users fork this repo, customize your-stack/ for their project,
# and commit everything to THEIR project repository.
# The entire .claude/ directory should be part of user projects.

# Generated task files (PRDs and task lists)
# These are auto-generated by /create-prd and /generate-tasks
.claude/tasks/
!.claude/tasks/.gitkeep

# ============================================
# Node.js
# ============================================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

